OL,4,Cyear-old's tractor death
OL,6,FA dad has denied unlawfully killing
OL,7,Fhis three-year-old son in a tractor
OL,8,Fincident.
OL,10,FAlbie Speakman died after being run
OL,11,Fover by a small tractor on farmland
OL,12,Foff Bentley Hall Road in Tottington,
OL,13,Fnear Bury, on 16 July 2022.
OL,15,FHe died before he could be taken to
OL,16,Fhospital.
