OL,3,CDad denies manslaughter after three-
OL,4,Cyear-old's tractor death
OL,6,FHis dad, Neil Speakman, 38, was
OL,7,Fcharged with gross negligence
OL,8,Fmanslaughter, and pleaded not guilty
OL,9,Fwhen he appeared at Manchester
OL,10,FMinshull Street Crown Court on 21 May.
OL,12,FSpeakman, of Bentley Hall Road, also
OL,13,Fdenied that on 16 July, as a self-
OL,14,Femployed person he failed to ensure,
OL,15,Fso far as was reasonably practicable,
OL,16,Fthe health and safety of Albie.
OL,18,FSpeakman will face trial on 14 January
OL,19,F2025.
