OL,6,FHe was bailed to attend a further case
OL,7,Fmanagement hearing on 2 December.
OL,9,FIn a statement issued at the time of
OL,10,Fhis death, Albie's mother, Leah, said:
OL,11,F"Albie was an incredibly loving,
OL,12,Faffectionate and caring boy who just
OL,13,Fwanted everyone to be happy.
OL,15,F"He was so sensitive and wanted
OL,16,Feveryone to be OK, especially the
OL,17,Fpeople that he loved."
